{"tid":1795930,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【鐵網圍封行人天橋】今晚是平安夜，包括紅磡海底隧道在內的多條交通要道上的天橋，都安裝密孔鐵網。","createTime":"2019-12-24T09:17:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T10:02:10.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a22e5138d1fde2db4d3c8339d3c902fc1bae114d","tid":1795930,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:17:06.000Z","msg":"【鐵網圍封行人天橋】今晚是平安夜，包括紅磡海底隧道在內的多條交通要道上的天橋，都安裝密孔鐵網。<br />\n<br />\n在紅隧港島出入口、告士打道上方、近伊利沙伯大廈的露天行人天橋上，架起方型的鐵網，鐵網近兩米高，頂部亦圍封，相信防止有人從天橋投擲物件，堵塞紅隧出入口。（相片由讀者提供）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ciJND8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FciJND8B.jpg&h=1b0ea364&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2724733130945623/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2724733130945623%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=IuE3y9gLaM%2BC%2BJZgSaDlpo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=ef322167\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2724733130945623/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"030e7ed9b95d46e1c578ff63cf4ecd29bc9f10d9","tid":1795930,"uid":45693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:19:24.000Z","msg":"🔒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f28cc97e972b0b6c039e0cabdb4b97cc5e577d70","tid":1795930,"uid":322044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 監獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f959243a94e14a7070753f25e06884d8471e1986","tid":1795930,"uid":11008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24T09:20:37.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，變撚左狗籠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd219d9736493dc0c3b67c6506cb5d095466171","tid":1795930,"uid":266672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-24